General description of the program: User chooses how far to cast his fishing rod,
then the user will have to wait a random amount of time before they catch something,
and are presented with their catch after they press the right button.
The user will be able to choose different bait that will attract different fish.
The program will keep track of the user's biggest fish caught and the rarest type of fish caught.
The user can quit the program at any time.
